{"tid":1707200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"胡錫進稱香港警員不用怕　背後有武警和解放軍可增援","createTime":"2019-11-11T09:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T16:21:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9214c3a6c406ccee9cb2b9e107f12d7cc8a01934","tid":1707200,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1491360_1_20191111164024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1491360_1_20191111164024.jpg&h=e0441daa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進在微博發文，堅決支持香港警員開槍擊倒圍攻暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進在文章指，香港的警員什麼都不用怕，說警員的身後不僅有愛國愛港的廣大香港民眾和全國民眾，更有武警和解放軍駐港部隊，在必要時他們隨時可以按照基本法規定，進入香港直接作出增援。<br />\n<br />\n他批評，這名警員一人面對多名暴徒，面臨被搶槍、暴打的威脅。他警告不得靠近，但後者無視警告。警員開槍回擊了現場暴徒的圍攻，也向香港其他暴徒發出明確信號，圍攻警員是要承擔包括被現場擊斃等各種法律風險。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進表示，一些香港和西方傳媒把焦點集中警員開槍，淡化暴徒的違法犯罪惡行，對這樣的輿論感到噁心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491360-20191111.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491360-20191111.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LL%2BPOpKvGkF1h1mPLRhV%2B8wxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=da846e28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491360-20191111.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=234da43c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491360-20191111.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"68fc9934903d27ff1f2709bff91b469e7b5ecc5b","tid":1707200,"uid":291626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"係就快d出解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe58f410264f0ba0ea4b78d189866e8aa1c2e5d","tid":1707200,"uid":62600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:34:52.000Z","msg":"對你淨係識口交仲嘔心"},{"pid":"653de3d0df835eb6be619f1e6557743491